Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.19,0:41:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.10,0:41:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.30,0:41:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.12,0:43:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.43,0:43:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,部长。我去商谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.60,0:43:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,和山本社长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.33,0:43:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.37,0:43:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话带他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.54,0:43:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我一个人可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.77,0:43:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是是很重要的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.87,0:43:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,多一个人比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.71,0:43:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.04,0:43:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那走吧\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.72,0:43:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是很重要的嘀谈喔\N拜托了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.63,0:43:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.45,0:44:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.26,0:44:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛这么紧张？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.16,0:44:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.73,0:44:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,被讨厌的男人用肉棒插了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.53,0:44:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.54,0:44:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.21,0:44:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.19,0:44:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.32,0:44:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,给我脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.66,0:45:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.37,0:45:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.54,0:45:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.11,0:45:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.98,0:45:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.69,0:45:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那时再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.42,0:45:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.79,0:45:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公的假日出勤今后会增加喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.37,0:45:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.04,0:45:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.03,0:46:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然穿得这么下流喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.43,0:46:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你也很想要了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.70,0:46:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.87,0:46:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,裙子也要脱掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.98,0:46:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.58,0:47:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.95,0:47:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来的话怎么办？\N那时候再说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.12,0:47:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.09,0:47:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快点做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.57,0:47:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.84,0:47:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤也脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.88,0:47:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.62,0:48:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.72,0:48:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,给我站好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.09,0:48:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,站好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.12,0:48:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.00,0:49:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,上次很舒服，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.43,0:49:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,才不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.10,0:49:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很容易湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.76,0:49:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,身体有反应咯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.53,0:49:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.87,0:49:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很讨厌被摸
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.37,0:49:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上次干得很过瘾吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.24,0:49:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是，放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.92,0:49:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.79,0:50:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.36,0:50:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要看你的身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.93,0:50:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚刚就好想要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.94,0:50:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.09,0:50:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要被摸吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.86,0:50:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.83,0:50:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种可能对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.77,0:50:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.64,0:50:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.75,0:50:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我没叫你那样做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.38,0:51:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,给我脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.65,0:51:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.30,0:51:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.57,0:51:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.51,0:51:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有听到我说脱掉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.99,0:52:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.00,0:52:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.17,0:52:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.70,0:52:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是公司耶
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.07,0:52:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,被人看到的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.98,0:52:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只有我看到，不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.25,0:52:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.72,0:52:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不做做看不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.99,0:52:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会很兴奋喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.03,0:52:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.96,0:52:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事不做不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.61,0:53:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然这样利用你手中的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.78,0:53:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,玩弄自己手下员工的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.59,0:53:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.09,0:53:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.03,0:53:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是现在常见的\N职场霸凌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.49,0:53:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.17,0:54:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.80,0:54:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那里也让我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.59,0:54:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.76,0:54:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.83,0:54:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,下面的嘴巴掰开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.04,0:54:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.57,0:54:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,粉红色的，好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.11,0:54:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这么漂亮的小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.55,0:54:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他每晚都想要做吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.92,0:54:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,做工作也能这样就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.80,0:55:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那和这个没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.43,0:55:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.54,0:55:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.24,0:55:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.88,0:55:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.03,0:55:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.23,0:55:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.64,0:55:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.01,0:55:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.95,0:56:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.05,0:56:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.86,0:56:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.33,0:56:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是星期五啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.77,0:56:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会看到这么溧亮的小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.38,0:56:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会很兴奋喔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.54,0:56:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好差劲，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.15,0:56:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.63,0:56:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.03,0:56:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.33,0:56:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.83,0:56:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.80,0:56:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.98,0:56:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和之前一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.75,0:57:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.46,0:57:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.26,0:57:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那样不行，这样也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.83,0:57:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.47,0:57:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要照我说的做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.01,0:57:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.62,0:57:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,知道怎么做吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.56,0:57:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.99,0:58:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那样不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.46,0:58:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那样做不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.03,0:59:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.01,0:59:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.61,0:59:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要更下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.08,0:59:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.17,0:59:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.70,0:59:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个当作老公的肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.07,0:59:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,会好好地吃老公的，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.04,0:59:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.92,0:59:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.15,0:59:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很讨厌你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.63,1:00:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了，快做啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.34,1:00:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.94,1:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司吃肉棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.74,1:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好差劲
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.95,1:00:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个不是偷偷交往了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.12,1:00:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,反正不都是在公司里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.86,1:00:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一样吗\N那不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.56,1:00:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不会这样做
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.43,1:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.16,1:00:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不会被像我这样的男人弄啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.17,1:00:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.29,1:01:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,差劲\N好兴奋了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.83,1:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.59,1:01:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.06,1:01:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.67,1:01:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那边很脏
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.40,1:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很脏才要你舔干净啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.32,1:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舒服的话
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.15,1:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.66,1:01:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.78,1:02:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好地做啦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.29,1:02:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点射出来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.16,1:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊，安静地做啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.63,1:02:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,说那种话就没兴致了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.15,1:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好做的话\N不知道会不会有人来喔
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.66,1:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.80,1:03:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N想要对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.80,1:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.15,1:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射了，射了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.92,1:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.55,1:04:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这边还有喔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.55,1:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏，住手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.45,1:04:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很脏才要清干净啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.00,1:04:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,变干净了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.21,1:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里插进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.74,1:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要..不要
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.44,1:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去喔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.41,1:04:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.55,1:04:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.48,1:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其实想要对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.56,1:05:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要让你很爽喔
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.12,1:05:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.82,1:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，住手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.67,1:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让我回去了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.64,1:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.21,1:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.24,1:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有人来的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.81,1:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再一下喔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.22,1:06:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，不要
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.96,1:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.03,1:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.67,1:06:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.97,1:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.54,1:06:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么那样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.30,1:06:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用那个
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.51,1:06:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.44,1:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公不一样吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.41,1:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我来让你爽啊\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.15,1:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.75,1:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让你去喔\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.45,1:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,插到深处喔
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.75,1:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.56,1:07:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样弄喔\N不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.33,1:07:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.23,1:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,差劲好，差劲
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.98,1:08:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.45,1:08:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.22,1:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还要喔\N这样不够吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.20,1:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.04,1:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.94,1:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.28,1:09:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.42,1:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.40,1:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.54,1:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再来喔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.18,1:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,来认真做喔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.95,1:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.22,1:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好好做啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.65,1:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我，放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.79,1:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.16,1:10:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.46,1:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.10,1:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.17,1:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.79,1:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.29,1:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.73,1:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要...住手
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.87,1:10:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.67,1:10:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.61,1:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.55,1:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.16,1:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.57,1:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊，还想要吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.24,1:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.24,1:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一次不够喔\N住手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.21,1:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.22,1:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N住手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.99,1:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.45,1:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.89,1:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.93,1:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这里去得好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.43,1:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到这么敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.60,1:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.20,1:11:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，住手啊\N怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.94,1:11:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要吗？\N不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.44,1:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,目前为止，没这样做过吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.18,1:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好差劲
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.12,1:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，要去了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.16,1:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.53,1:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.36,1:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.16,1:12:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.19,1:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我很兴奋了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.69,1:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.06,1:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,想去就去吧\N不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.46,1:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.37,1:13:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,想去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.84,1:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.10,1:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样插喔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.81,1:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.74,1:13:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了啦\N小穴要去了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.05,1:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.42,1:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.03,1:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.20,1:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.50,1:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.14,1:21:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.08,1:21:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.45,1:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了，要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.92,1:21:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.21,1:22:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.48,1:22:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.42,1:22:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行...不行
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.75,1:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.72,1:22:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.24,1:23:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.42,1:23:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来没发烧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.16,1:23:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.46,1:23:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟部长说的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.44,1:24:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起喔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.92,1:24:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.02,1:24:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,早安\N早安
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.26,1:24:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个\N是
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.86,1:24:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你太太身体不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.49,1:24:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.83,1:24:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.60,1:24:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.47,1:24:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.27,1:24:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,平常一直叫你们去，抱歉喔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.94,1:24:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.84,1:24:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.51,1:24:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.21,1:24:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.08,1:24:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.55,1:24:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦了\N这边拜托咯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.07,1:25:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,来休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.38,1:25:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好差劲
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.41,1:25:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.38,1:26:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.99,1:26:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,随我喜欢的弄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.03,1:26:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种事
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.26,1:26:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.26,1:26:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.33,1:26:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢被反抗啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.97,1:26:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然做这样的事
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.04,1:26:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.22,1:26:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很讨厌吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.82,1:27:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.43,1:27:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,被讨厌的男人碰
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.50,1:27:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只能安静了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.44,1:27:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个身体要慢慢享用了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.54,1:27:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你等很久了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.05,1:27:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种可能吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.52,1:27:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴上说得好听
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.60,1:27:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.86,1:27:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,身体是诚实的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.30,1:28:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.91,1:28:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.11,1:28:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.62,1:28:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被碰
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.72,1:28:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,都说不要被摸了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.33,1:28:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.86,1:28:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越老实了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.10,1:28:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.71,1:28:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,原来这么色啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.55,1:28:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.29,1:28:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,其实一直在等我吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.40,1:29:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.83,1:29:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是偶尔而已
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.97,1:29:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔喔
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.71,1:29:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.34,1:29:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔而已
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.41,1:29:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是这样吗？\N当然
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.25,1:29:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔会这样期待啊\N对..对
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.99,1:29:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,偶然而已\N可能是在等着我来干吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.36,1:29:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好像变热了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.76,1:29:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.26,1:29:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.90,1:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很兴奋了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.53,1:30:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老公那边不太行
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.50,1:30:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这样弄
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.77,1:30:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.74,1:30:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还会做更多喔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.28,1:30:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这样被女人说了，好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.25,1:31:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.97,1:31:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,咸咸的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.64,1:31:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,朝这边
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.88,1:32:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.94,1:33:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.15,1:33:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公还棒
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.93,1:33:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌你这样的人了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.34,1:33:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.45,1:34:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.65,1:34:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.95,1:35:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌我了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.68,1:35:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然被我弄得这么兴奋了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.05,1:35:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.27,1:35:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,才不舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.47,1:35:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,换你咯
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.61,1:36:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,换你这家伙来帮我弄啦
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.00,1:36:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.46,1:36:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,来让我爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.47,1:36:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是很温柔的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.11,1:36:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舔啊...舔啊...来舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.08,1:36:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.91,1:36:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想要这个
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.98,1:37:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然会想要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.78,1:37:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没这种事的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.48,1:37:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么样？说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.12,1:37:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,给我你那肮脏的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.19,1:37:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好...好
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.30,1:37:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.71,1:37:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要这个啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.82,1:37:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想要就要说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.79,1:37:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.09,1:37:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.83,1:37:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因为很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.95,1:38:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.15,1:38:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好色啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.05,1:38:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.05,1:38:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吵
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.59,1:38:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌的你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.66,1:39:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有办法好好舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.80,1:39:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.47,1:40:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.64,1:40:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很脏吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.51,1:40:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.99,1:40:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.09,1:40:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌的男人的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.44,1:40:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要被操啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.28,1:40:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.09,1:41:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.27,1:41:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.27,1:41:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.63,1:41:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.30,1:41:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮你好好舔
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.88,1:42:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.05,1:42:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要...要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.52,1:43:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快点插啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.82,1:43:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.85,1:43:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.79,1:43:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.33,1:44:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.33,1:44:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,插进了我的小穴喔
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.74,1:44:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.47,1:44:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N其实是很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.11,1:44:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看你都爽成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.25,1:44:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都确实插进小穴里了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.69,1:45:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.27,1:45:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.62,1:45:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要做的吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.39,1:45:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人..骗人
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.66,1:45:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想要插
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.86,1:45:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.39,1:45:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.27,1:45:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.03,1:45:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.88,1:45:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去的地方看得很清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.65,1:46:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要那样摸
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.95,1:46:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.66,1:46:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不能那样，停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.16,1:46:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不动你也会动啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.82,1:46:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.90,1:46:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.50,1:46:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.00,1:46:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.17,1:46:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.47,1:47:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.20,1:47:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那里，那里不行
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.17,1:47:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是你要的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.28,1:47:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.65,1:47:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.59,1:47:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.79,1:47:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拔出来喔
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.06,1:47:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了...去了...去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.88,1:48:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你不起来我不知道怎么做喔
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.07,1:48:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.46,1:49:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.27,1:49:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要...要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.67,1:49:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.80,1:49:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.12,1:49:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出来，拔出来，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.79,1:49:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这样不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.03,1:49:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.43,1:49:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.30,1:49:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了...去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.41,1:50:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.61,1:50:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这样插了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.82,1:50:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了，吵死了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.86,1:50:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出来
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.06,1:50:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.14,1:50:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,被最讨厌的肉棒插着
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.51,1:50:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会很爽的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.44,1:51:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.98,1:51:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.82,1:51:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...不要...不要...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.46,1:51:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.23,1:51:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.47,1:51:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...要去了...不要
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.92,1:52:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这样插进去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.09,1:52:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.09,1:52:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.07,1:52:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.73,1:52:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要装得这么可怜嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.17,1:52:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去咯
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.75,1:53:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.38,1:53:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这样插那里
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.23,1:53:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了，拔出来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.23,1:53:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,变得很奇怪了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.64,1:53:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出来是不是才不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.19,1:53:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.22,1:53:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,去了...去了...去了...去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.03,1:54:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.00,1:54:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.47,1:54:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就射给你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.97,1:54:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.47,1:54:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.08,1:54:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.64,1:54:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.72,1:54:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.36,1:54:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.61,1:54:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.01,1:54:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,住手了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.72,1:54:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.95,1:54:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.01,1:55:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.40,1:55:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然被最讨厌的男人\N玩成这样
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.04,1:55:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是绝对不能跟老公说的事
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.81,1:55:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是我变得很糟糕了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.26,1:56:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以拜托你处理一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.33,1:56:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.17,1:56:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想拜托你和我一起处理
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.20,1:57:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.61,1:57:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我成了最讨厌男人的精液便器
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.58,1:57:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只是为了释放性欲
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.12,1:57:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但我依然臣服在他的肉棒之下
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.96,1:57:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,（导演   朝雾净）
